  ('0f6n1HMHI6g', 122, 139, ARRAY['symphony if at all possible, so we''ll see how that goes. All right, so it starts at El De Gretto, 96. That''s the metronome marking. And this little pits, there are two of them and there''s a little circle with a line up.', 'And so what that means is a Bartok pits, which basically means and this is how I do the Bartok pits, there may be different ways to do it.']::text[]),
  ('0f6n1HMHI6g', 139, 152, ARRAY['basically means and this is how I do the Bartok pits, there may be different ways to do it. I take my two fingers, my thumb and my first finger and I pinch the string and then I pull up very slightly and then let go.', 'I''ll do that again, ready? Now don''t pull too high. If you pull too high, first of all you''re going to go out and pitch and second of all']::text[]),
  ('0f6n1HMHI6g', 152, 169, ARRAY['up very slightly and then let go. I''ll do that again, ready? Now don''t pull too high. If you pull too high, first of all you''re going to go out and pitch and second of all you might snap your string.', 'So not too high, maybe like, oh I don''t know, about this much up and down. I don''t know how much that is, maybe an inch? Well, that''s probably too high. So half an inch, how about?']::text[]),
  ('0f6n1HMHI6g', 163, 180, ARRAY['up and down. I don''t know how much that is, maybe an inch? Well, that''s probably too high. So half an inch, how about? And then what that does is it gives a snap.', 'The string comes down and snaps back against the fingerboard slightly. And if you do that with 40 violins as well as all the other instruments, then it makes a pretty cool little slap sound.']::text[]),
  ('0f6n1HMHI6g', 180, 209, ARRAY['So, when we first start off, we hear the lower strings do this pit, and then we do it. So it goes lower strings, so boom, boom, and then after the fermata, now it''s the other way around.', 'It''s us first, and then the lower strings, and then we go lower strings. Okay, so I''ll do that one more time. So boom, and then boom. Does that make sense?']::text[]),
  ('0f6n1HMHI6g', 210, 225, ARRAY['So it''s lower strings, then us, us and lower strings, and this is the first violin part, by the way. Okay, and then you have this ...', 'All these trills and so forth, and we''re doing this with the clarinets and a couple of the other woodwinds, as far as I know, and so we don''t have to overplay this.']::text[]),
  ('0f6n1HMHI6g', 225, 242, ARRAY['have to overplay this.', 'The most important part that I can see is the accent, so it''s the beginning of your note, and also don''t push too hard because there''s a lot coming up after this beginning, and so save your strength, because you want to be able to play the rest of it, and p...']::text[]),
